description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Due to internal progression an opportunity has arisen for a Rotational Pharmacy Assistant to join our forward thinking, patient focused team based at Northern Devon Healthcare Trust. The post is suitable for an individual looking for variety within hospital pharmacy. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The rotation includes the Dispensary, Procurement, Aseptic Services and Distribution. Applicants should have good IT and time management skills, good communication and organisational skills, be a team player and preferably have pharmaceutical experience, however this is not essential. Training will be given to the successful candidate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be required to participate in the weekend (Saturday and Sunday) and Bank Holiday rotas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that this vacancy will close as soon as sufficient applications have been received&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further information please contact Maria Phillips mariaphillips1@nhs.net 01271 322395.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date 13th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
